OL,3,CElective surgeries postponed as
OL,4,CGuernsey hospital reaches capacity
OL,6,FThe has announced some elective
OL,7,Fsurgeries will be postponed as the
OL,8,FPrincess Elizabeth Hospital has
OL,9,Freached full capacity.
OL,11,FOverall, 19 elective surgeries will be
OL,12,Fdelayed, including 13 orthopaedic and
OL,13,Fsix general operations.
OL,15,FFurther disruptions may still affect
OL,16,Felective surgeries in the coming days,
OL,17,Fbut emergency surgeries will be
OL,18,Fprioritised.
