OL,4,CGuernsey hospital reaches capacity
OL,6,FHSC stated: "We recognise it is always
OL,7,Fdisappointing when elective surgery
OL,8,Fhas to be postponed and apologises for
OL,9,Fthe impact this has on individuals and
OL,10,Ftheir families."
OL,12,F"There is no single factor impacting
OL,13,Fon acute care and it is a seasonal
OL,14,Fissue with demand outstripping
OL,15,Favailable capacity.
OL,17,F"Teams have worked tirelessly to
OL,18,Fminimise the number of postponed
OL,19,Felective surgeries."
